message: Initial commit
ci: add pre-commit check
docs: add "README.md"
docs: change the TensorBay link from ".com" to ".cn" in "README.md"

refactor!: rename and remove all functions which ends with "_object(s)"

Changes:
- `upload_dataset_object` -> `upload_dataset`
- `upload_segment_object` -> `upload_segment`
- `upload_sensor_object` -> `upload_sensor`
- `upload_data` -> `upload_file`
- `upload_data_object` -> `upload_data`
- `upload_frame_object` -> `upload_frame`
- `list_data` -> `list_data_paths`
- `list_data_objects` -> `list_data`
- `list_frame_objects` -> `list_frames`
- `get_segment_object` -> Remove, use `Segment.__init__` instead.
docs: use black to format the "Read images from the Dataset" docs

docs: add the sphinx full documentation site to the "README.md"
docs: update all graviti official webpages urls in docs and "README.md"

rather than `DatasetClient`
